def test_sanitize_vector_name_fallback_rules():
    out = sanitize_vector_name("org/model_name__v2")
    assert "/" not in out
    assert "_" not in out
    assert len(out) <= 64
    assert re.match(r"^[a-z0-9\-]+$", out)
